      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_2176417" metaid="metaid_97" name="SMAD7:NEDD4L complex translocates to the cytosol" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Binding of NEDD4L promotes translocation of SMAD7 to the cytosol (Kuratomi et al. 2005). This is based on experiments using recombinant mouse Smad7 and recombinant human NEDD4L.</p>
        </notes>
