      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_2187375" metaid="metaid_98" name="SMAD3 binds STUB1 (CHIP)" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">STUB1 (CHIP), an E3 ubiquitin ligase, binds SMAD3 irrespective of TGF-beta stimulation (Li et al. 2004, Xin et al. 2005).</p>
