      <reaction compartment="compartment_947587" fast="false" id="reaction_170835" metaid="metaid_99" name="An anchoring protein, ZFYVE9 (SARA), recruits SMAD2/3" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">The activated TGF-beta receptor complex is internalized by clathrin-mediated endocytosis into early endosomes. ZFYVE9 (SARA) resides in the membrane of early endosomes. Crystallographic studies suggest that dimeric SARA in the early endosome coordinates two R-SMAD molecules (SMAD2 and/or SMAD3) per one receptor complex.</p>
        </notes>
        <annotation>
          <rdf:RDF xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:vCard="http://www.w3.org/2001/vcard-rdf/3.0#" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:bqbiol="http://biomodels.net/biology-qualifiers/">
            <rdf:Description rdf:about="#metaid_99">
              <dc:creator>
                <rdf:Bag>
                  <rdf:li rdf:parseType="Resource">
                    <vCard:N rdf:parseType="Resource">
                      <vCard:Family>Jassal</vCard:Family>
                      <vCard:Given>Bijay</vCard:Given>
                    </vCard:N>
                    <vCard:ORG rdf:parseType="Resource">
