      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_2176445" metaid="metaid_108" name="SMURF2 binds SMAD2" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">SMURF2 binds SMAD2 irrespective of TGF-beta signaling (Zhang et al. 2001).</p>
