      <reaction compartment="compartment_7660" fast="false" id="reaction_2167924" metaid="metaid_111" name="SMAD7:SMURF1 complex binds XPO1 (CRM1)" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">SMAD7:SMURF1 complex binds to XPO1 (CRM1) through a nuclear export signal (NES) located in the C-terminus of SMURF1 (Tajima et al. 2003). Recombinant mouse Smad7 and recombinant human SMURF1 were used in this study.</p>
        </notes>
