      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_2187368" metaid="metaid_118" name="STUB1 (CHIP) ubiquitinates SMAD3" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">STUB1 (CHIP) ubiquitinates SMAD3 in the absence of TGF-beta stimulation (Li et al. 2004, Xin et al. 2005).</p>
