      <reaction compartment="compartment_7660" fast="false" id="reaction_2167876" metaid="metaid_119" name="SMAD7:SMURF2 complex translocates to the cytosol" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">After forming a complex in the nucleus, SMAD7:SMURF2 traffics to the cytosol (Kavsak et al. 2000). This was inferred from experiments that used a recombinant mouse Smad7 and recombinant human SMURF2.</p>
        </notes>
