      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_2187355" metaid="metaid_125" name="PMEPA1 sequesters phosphorylated SMAD2/3" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">PMEPA1 binds phosphorylated SMAD2 and SMAD3, preventing formation of SMAD2/3:SMAD4 heterotrimers (Watanabe et al. 2010).</p>
        </notes>
