      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_2187401" metaid="metaid_134" name="MTMR4 dephosphorylates SMAD2/3" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">MTMR4 protein phosphatase dephosphorylates SMAD2 and SMAD3, preventing formation of SMAD2/3:SMAD4 heterotrimers and inhibiting transmission of TGF-beta signal to the nucleus (Yu et al. 2010).</p>
        </notes>
