      <reaction compartment="compartment_70101" fast="false" id="reaction_2187358" metaid="metaid_140" name="PMEPA1 sequesters unphosphorylated SMAD2/3" reversible="false">
        <notes>
          <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">PMEPA1 binds unphosphorylated SMAD2 and SMAD3 and prevents their phosphorylation in response to TGF-beta stimulation (Watanabe et al. 2010).</p>
